snippet.title: Splatoon 3 – Release Date Revealed  - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
INKoming! Splatoon 3 splashes down on Nintendo Switch September 9th!  Get an early look at the game with this fresh Turf War gameplay!

Pre-order available now:
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/splatoon-3-switch/
